  <brief_title>BAROSTIM THERAPY™ In Heart Failure With Preserved Ejection Fraction</brief_title>
  <acronym>HFpEF</acronym>
  <official_title>BAROSTIM THERAPY ™ in Heart Failure With Preserved Ejection Fraction: A Post-Market Registry With the CE-Marked BAROSTIM NEO™ System</official_title>
